{"type": "article", "id": 3978, "title": "by | n香氛", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-01T07:46:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233223C80bLYnSJ3FVGuOk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t别人家的香氛大多数是以独特的香味吸引顾客，而日本 Nendo 设计工作室为旗下品牌 by | n 设计的香氛则是以其设计感取胜。日前，设计团队带来了两款全新的家用香氛，一款名为「Feather Pen 」，正如其名，这款香氛被设计为传统的羽毛笔的样子，木质的羽毛笔插入装着香氛的小瓶，用来挥发瓶中的香气。另一款名为「Bubbles」,Nendo 将弥漫在房间里的香味想像为一个一个的肥皂泡，于是将将压缩后的毛毡运用激光切割的方式将其制作成气泡的图案，趣味十足。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233220A8Ve2YMC0WK5BFaL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052332207uJ3dkcqTS8yLrMp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233221ZJ8XBa3PdG5wRhr4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233221BPmz7xeAwrq3MYoX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052332223JZE8gedUPn4sGcj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}